    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币软件升级以增加新功能引发激烈争论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/bitcoin-debate-heats-up-over-software-revamp-to-add-new-features</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着通过软件升级代码添加新功能的努力不断推进，比特币区块链作为主要支持数字黄金的网络的声誉可能会发生变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/bitcoin-debate-heats-up-over-software-revamp-to-add-new-features</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国芯片出口引领贸易增长 助推经济发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/south-korea-s-chip-exports-lead-trade-gains-supporting-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在半导体需求的带动下，韩国出口上个月持续增长，推动该国贸易平衡达到 2020 年以来的最大顺差，并支持政策制定者对今年经济扩张好于预期的乐观态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/south-korea-s-chip-exports-lead-trade-gains-supporting-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 00:39:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ualá 首席运营官将离开拉丁美洲金融科技公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/uala-chief-operating-officer-is-leaving-latin-american-fintech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，长期担任高盛集团银行家的玛丽安娜·弗兰扎 (Mariana Franza) 三年前接任阿根廷金融科技公司 Ualá 的首席运营官，现在她将离开该公司以寻求其他机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/uala-chief-operating-officer-is-leaving-latin-american-fintech</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 00:34:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登否决国会废除 SEC 加密货币指导的提议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/biden-vetos-congressional-bid-to-void-sec-crypto-guidance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登否决了一项国会决议，该决议将推翻美国证券交易委员会的指导方针，加密货币行业称该指导方针阻碍了其与银行合作的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/biden-vetos-congressional-bid-to-void-sec-crypto-guidance</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 00:05:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
